dct_title_s: Kossuth County, Iowa, 1975, aerial photomosaic index
dct_description_sm: Title supplied by cataloger based on information from sheet labels. Images are photoreductions of mosaics created from original aerial photographs. Designating symbol 19109. Form of individual image numbering: 19109-175-[number]. Year flown: 1975. Flown by Toler Aerial Mapping Co. Odessa, Texas. Scale 1:38,000
